Description: Provides tools to read, process, visualize, and download
    hydrological, climatic, physiographic, metadata, and geospatial
    data from the CAMELS-PE dataset (Catchment Attributes and
    Meteorology for Large-sample Studies - Peru). The package is
    designed to work with externally stored CAMELS-PE data and does
    not include the dataset itself. Functions support reading daily
    time series, catchment attributes, station metadata, metadata
    dictionaries, geospatial layers, and basic visualization of time
    series and catchment boundaries. CAMELS-PE data are available at
    <doi:10.5281/zenodo.20058779> and package documentation is
    available at <https://hllauca.github.io/RCamelsPE/>.
